title: fanoutqa: Who are the five cast members with the longest tenures on Saturday Night Live (SNL), and what are their respective birth years? (07381c55a61df50a)

chat_history.content: Who are the five cast members with the longest tenures on Saturday Night Live (SNL), and what are their respective birth years?

Here are the five cast members with the longest tenures on Saturday Night Live (SNL), along with their birth years:

1. Darrell Hammond (1955): 14 seasons (1995-2009)
2. Kenan Thompson (1978): 14 seasons (2003-2016) and still a current cast member
3. Fred Armisen (1966): 11 seasons (2002-2013)
4. Seth Meyers (1973): 11 seasons (2001-2014)
5. Tim Meadows (1961): 10 seasons (1991-2000)
